Class AbstractElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • teal.core.AbstractElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, HasID, TElement, THasPropertyChange
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Colorizer, CreateAtPick, CylindricalField, DLICGenerator, Rendered, Scalar, SimEngine, SimObj, Simulation3D, VectorGenerator, WaveGenerator

    public abstract class AbstractElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements TElement
    This class is the base for all T Objects that are not extended from a Java class. Each TObj class will provide accessor methods for any attribute.
